{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_017EEhEdLcPHYMjRedMsFEu8","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Two problems found:\n1. `app-user` has **empty `configure`** permission in `/app` → can't declare the queue (the not_authorised error).\n2. A `force-quorum` policy in `/app` forces `queue-type: quorum`, which would override the queue to quorum, violating the \"classic\" requirement.\n\nLet me fix both via rabbitmqctl (durable, no data loss)."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1353,"cache_read_input_tokens":28462,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1353},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0b925a52-fb46-47f3-8164-dca48bf94d2f","uuid":"335ad688-71ff-4e11-8b83-a75002a80ae5","request_id":"req_011CcAXtVVAWaKaQfaKDqS4U"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_017EEhEdLcPHYMjRedMsFEu8","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01VnCUcdfmKDKZkfEEWpXer3","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"NS=karma-rabbitmq-classic-queue-20260618-100020\nAPP_USER=$(kubectl -n $NS get secret rabbitmq-app -o jsonpath='{.data.username}' | base64 -d)\necho \"app user: $APP_USER\"\n# Grant configure permission so app-user can declare its queue\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl set_permissions -p /app \"$APP_USER\" \".*\" \".*\" \".*\"\necho \"--- delete quorum-forcing policy in /app ---\"\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl clear_policy -p /app force-quorum\necho \"--- verify perms ---\"\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl list_permissions -p /app\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl list_policies -p /app","description":"Grant configure perm and remove quorum policy"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1353,"cache_read_input_tokens":28462,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1353},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0b925a52-fb46-47f3-8164-dca48bf94d2f","uuid":"aaa0c1ba-fea0-4c59-967d-7d4a2ac67c10","request_id":"req_011CcAXtVVAWaKaQfaKDqS4U"}
